# Dependencies & build artifacts (rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage

# Secrets & local env — never bake into an image layer
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# VCS / CI / editor
.git
.github
.gitignore
**/.vscode
**/.idea

# Local-only files
**/*.log
uploads/
RUNBOOK.md
repomix-output.*

# OS
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
